<h1 class="title">Invite your customers</h1>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-9">
    <div class="alert alert-info" role="alert">
      <h4>Trustpilot Company Guidelines:</h4>
      <p>All consumers must be invited equally, without exception, to leave a review about their purchase experience.
        Reviews, in turn, should always reflect that experience accurately.</p>
      <br />
      <p><b><%= link_to 'Click here to read more', guidelines_path %></b></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<p>Invite your customers by providing us with these customer details: email address, name and reference ID.
  Select a file (.csv or .txt), copy paste your data or enter it manually.</p>

<br />

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-2"><input type="text" class="btn btn-info" value="Select a file" /></div>
  <div class="col-md-2 col-md-offset-2">
    <%= link_to 'Copy paste', send_invitations_copy_paste_index_path, :class => 'btn btn-info' %>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-2 col-md-offset-1">
    <%= link_to 'Enter manually', send_invitations_add_invites_path, :class => 'btn btn-info' %>
  </div>
</div>